Core Models:
User — Standalone (email, name, phone)
Lead — Central model (form submissions, personal/employment/loan info)
Application — Created from Lead (status, BRE integration)
Offer — Loan offers for Applications
Consent — Consent records for Leads
BreSession — BRE processing sessions for Applications
FormAbandonment — Tracks abandoned form sessions
AnalyticsEvent — Analytics events
Relationships:

Lead → Application (1:N) — leadId in Application
Application → Offer (1:N) — applicationId in Offer
Application → BreSession (1:N) — applicationId in BreSession
Lead → Consent (1:N) — leadId in Consent
Lead → FormAbandonment (1:N, optional) — leadId in FormAbandonment
Lead → AnalyticsEvent (1:N, optional) — leadId in AnalyticsEvent
Flow: Lead → Application → Offer/BreSession. Consent and analytics track Lead interactions.
